# Pickomino

This repository contains a game simulator for the dice game [Pickomino](https://boardgamegeek.com/boardgame/15818/pickomino)
(also known as Heckmeck am Bratwurmeck). The simulator can be used to calculate the expected value of a given strategy.
There are also some predefined strategies that can be used.

### First steps

See [GameHelper](https://github.com/bartek-wesolowski/pickomino/blob/main/src/main/kotlin/com/bartoszwesolowski/pickomino/GameHelper.kt)
and [GameSeriesSimulator](https://github.com/bartek-wesolowski/pickomino/blob/main/src/main/kotlin/com/bartoszwesolowski/pickomino/GameSeriesSimulator.kt).